         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[To his excellency] Calpurnius [Concessus, epistrategos], from [Gemellus also called Horion, son of Gaius Apolinarius], Antinoite. [Of the petition which I submitted to the most illustrious prefect], Aemilius [Saturninus, and of the sacred subscription which I obtained from him, I have appended a copy. - - -]</ab>
